Damask rose mist 🌹
It’s very refreshing and love the smell of the mist. Can be used before the make up and spray it after completing the makeup to set the makeup. 

24k gold elixir✨ 
It can be mixed with the makeup or directly applied on the face before applying the foundation to give a dewy and luminous finish to the makeup. 
Contains: pumpkin seed oil, Rosa rubiginosa seed oil, tocopherol acetate, almond oil, rose oil and swarna varq. 

Naftint 💄
Very pigmented and easy to apply. The product stays longer on the face. It can be removed only using cleansing oil/ balm.

Know more 👇

Keravive scalp treatment is similar to hydrafacial. They used antidandruff shampoo, led therapy and gave me a deep cleanse. 

MNRF ( microneedling + radiofrequency) is used to boost collagen production, treats pitted scars. The downtime is longer. 

Led therapy for scalp - I did not see much difference. I’ve tried only twice, it’s too early to comment on this.
